<body class="paged-page page-sources">
  <header class="topbar"><div class="brand">YUZURU HANYU <span>ICE LEGACY</span></div><nav><a href="index.html" data-paged-link="home">生涯总览／里程碑</a><a href="profile.html" data-paged-link="profile">个人主页</a><a href="competition.html" data-paged-link="competition">比赛档案</a><a href="shows.html" data-paged-link="shows">职业冰演</a><a href="costumes.html" data-paged-link="costumes">考斯滕</a><a href="sources.html" data-paged-link="sources">官方网站</a></nav><div class="source-chip"></div></header>
<section class="hero"><div class="hero-bg"></div><div class="producer-credit">&#21046;&#20316;&#20154; &#183; momoka1207</div><div class="orbit"></div><div class="hero-content"><div class="kicker">A DIGITAL EXHIBITION · 1994—2026</div><h1>羽生结弦<small>FROM COMPETITION TO ICE STORY</small></h1><p class="hero-copy">沿着比赛、纪录、冬奥荣耀与职业冰演的轨迹，观看一个运动员如何不断拓展冰上表达的边界。</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="btn primary" href="shows.html">进入职业冰演展厅</a><a class="btn" href="#overview">探索关键里程碑</a></div></div><a class="hero-credit" href="https://www.afpbb.com/articles/-/3162907" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Photo: AFP / Javier Soriano · PyeongChang 2018 medal ceremony</a><div class="hero-stats"><div class="hero-stat"><b>102</b><span>比赛记录</span></div><div class="hero-stat"><b>62</b><span>冠军次数</span></div><div class="hero-stat"><b>87</b><span>领奖台次数</span></div><div class="hero-stat"><b>2</b><span>冬奥单人金牌</span></div><div class="hero-stat"><b>36</b><span>职业冰演场次</span></div></div></section>

  <main>
    <section id="overview" class="section wrap overview-milestone">
  <div class="section-head"><div><div class="section-label">Life trajectory & milestones</div><h2>从仙台到世界，从竞技到 ICE STORY</h2></div><p class="section-intro">这里把生涯总览与关键里程碑合并成一座前厅：先看他如何穿越少年、成年组、冬奥、世界纪录与职业创作，再进入完整比赛档案和职业冰演宇宙。</p></div>
  <div class="overview-fusion">
    <article class="glass life-axis-panel">
      <div class="section-label">Arc of the legacy</div>
      <h3>一条不是直线的冰上轨迹</h3>
      <p>竞技记录在 2009 年进入高密度阶段；2014 与 2018 的冬奥金牌把名字推向世界中心；2022 年后，数据重心转向由本人主导的个人冰演与叙事型 ICE STORY。这里不再只是一张统计图，而是一条不断拓展表达边界的生命轨道。</p>
      <div class="axis-steps"><span>1994 仙台</span><span>1999 开始滑冰</span><span>2014 / 2018 冬奥</span><span>2022 职业转向</span><span>2026 仍在延展</span></div>
    </article>
    <article class="glass insight fusion-stats"><div><div class="section-label">Peak signals</div><div class="big">330.43</div><h3>竞技峰值与职业峰值并置</h3><p>最高总分、世界纪录与职业冰演场次共同构成这座数字展馆的主骨架。</p></div><div class="mini-list"><div class="mini"><span>世界纪录标记</span><b>19</b></div><div class="mini"><span>2024 职业冰演场次</span><b>13</b></div><div class="mini"><span>当前比赛档案</span><b>102 条</b></div></div></article>
    <article class="glass chart-panel compact-signal"><div class="chart-head"><div><h3>年度活动信号</h3><p>比赛记录与职业冰演场次</p></div><div class="legend"><span style="--c:#55c7f2">比赛</span><span style="--c:#f1874b">职业冰演</span></div></div><div id="trend" class="chart"></div></article>
  </div>
  <div class="milestone-integrated-head">
    <div><div class="section-label">Milestones & records</div><h3>关键里程碑</h3></div>
    <div class="milestone-controls"><div id="milestoneCount" class="section-label"></div><div class="filters" id="milestoneFilters"><button class="filter active" data-mile-filter="all">全部</button><button class="filter" data-mile-filter="人生">人生</button><button class="filter" data-mile-filter="竞技">竞技</button><button class="filter" data-mile-filter="纪录">纪录</button><button class="filter" data-mile-filter="职业">职业</button></div></div>
  </div>
  <div id="milestoneGrid" class="milestone-grid"></div>
</section>
<!-- MUSEUM_V3_SECTIONS -->
<section id="profile" class="section wrap">
  <div class="section-head"><div><div class="section-label">The person behind the legend</div><h2>一个人的时间，如何成为一代人的星光</h2></div><p class="section-intro">从仙台的少年，到两届冬奥冠军，再到以身体、文字、音乐与冰面构筑世界的创作者。这一页记录成绩之外的生命轨迹。</p></div>
  <div class="profile-grid">
    <article class="glass portrait-panel"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="assets/inline-00-316656306a.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" id="profilePortrait" alt="羽生结弦《SEIMEI》晴明考斯滕举手比一"><div class="portrait-caption"><div class="section-label">Sendai · 1994.12.07</div><h3>羽生结弦</h3><div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:11px">YUZURU HANYU · PROFESSIONAL ATHLETE / CREATOR</div></div><a class="portrait-credit" href="https://number.bunshun.jp/articles/-/847025?page=1" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Photo: Tsutomu Kishimoto / JMPA · Number Web</a></article>
    <article class="glass profile-copy"><div class="section-label">Biography</div><p class="lead">他的轨迹并不是一条只通向奖牌的直线。它穿过伤病、震灾、世界纪录与万众注视，也穿过一次次重新理解“为何滑冰”的时刻。竞技时代结束以后，冰面没有成为过去——它被扩展成剧场、记忆、祈愿与仍在书写的未来。</p>
      <div class="life-line"><b>1994</b><span>出生于宫城县仙台市。</span><b>1999</b><span>开始学习花样滑冰。</span><b>2004</b><span>现有比赛档案的起点。</span><b>2014 / 2018</b><span>连续两届获得冬奥会男子单人滑金牌。</span><b>2022</b><span>结束竞技生涯，转为职业运动员。</span><b>2022—2026</b><span>以 PROLOGUE、GIFT、RE_PRAY、Echoes of Life、REALIVE 等作品拓展 ICE STORY。</span></div>
      <div class="socials"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@hanyuyuzuru2624" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">YouTube ↗</a><a href="https://x.com/YUZURUofficial_" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">X / Official Staff ↗</a><a href="https://www.instagram.com/yuzuruofficial_/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Instagram ↗</a><a href="https://www.olympics.com/en/athletes/yuzuru-hanyu" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Olympics Profile ↗</a></div>
      <div class="countdown"><div class="countdown-title"><span>距离下一次 12 月 7 日</span><span id="birthdayYear"></span></div><div class="countdown-clock"><div class="count-unit"><b id="countDays">--</b><span>Days</span></div><div class="count-unit"><b id="countHours">--</b><span>Hours</span></div><div class="count-unit"><b id="countMinutes">--</b><span>Minutes</span></div><div class="count-unit"><b id="countSeconds">--</b><span>Seconds</span></div></div></div><div class="countdown july19-countdown" id="july19Countdown"><div class="countdown-title"><span id="july19NextTitle">距离下一次 7 月 19 日</span><span id="july19Year"></span></div><div class="countdown-clock"><div class="count-unit"><b id="july19Days">--</b><span>天</span></div><div class="count-unit"><b id="july19Hours">--</b><span>小时</span></div><div class="count-unit"><b id="july19Minutes">--</b><span>分钟</span></div><div class="count-unit"><b id="july19Seconds">--</b><span>秒</span></div></div></div><div class="countdown july19-since" id="july19Since"><div class="countdown-title"><span id="july19SinceTitle">距离 2022 年 7 月 19 日已经过去</span><span id="july19AnniversaryLabel">转职纪念日</span></div><div class="countdown-clock single"><div class="count-unit"><b id="sinceJuly19Days">--</b><span>天</span></div></div></div>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="profile-books" id="profileBooks">
    <div class="profile-books-head">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label" id="profileBooksLabel">著作与自述</div>
        <h3 id="profileBooksTitle">《苍炎》自传系列</h3>
      </div>
      <p id="profileBooksIntro">四卷自传以照片与长篇访谈记录竞技生涯、震灾后的重建、两届冬奥征程，以及转为职业运动员后继续创作 ICE STORY 的过程。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-books-grid" id="profileBooksGrid">
      <article class="glass profile-book-card" data-book-index="0">
        <div class="profile-book-cover"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="./aoi-hono-cover-01.jpg?v=20260717b" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='./assets/book-aoi-hono-1.jpg?v=20260717b';" alt="《苍炎》封面"></div>
        <div class="profile-book-copy"><div class="profile-book-meta" id="profileBookMeta0">第 1 卷 · 2012 · 扶桑社</div><h4 id="profileBookTitle0">《苍炎》</h4><p id="profileBookDesc0">以照片和长篇访谈回顾从4岁开始滑冰、经历2011年东日本大地震，到首次站上世界锦标赛领奖台前后的成长。</p></div>
      </article>
      <article class="glass profile-book-card" data-book-index="1">
        <div class="profile-book-cover"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="./aoi-hono-cover-02.jpg?v=20260717b" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='./assets/book-aoi-hono-2.jpg?v=20260717b';" alt="《苍炎Ⅱ：飞翔篇》封面"></div>
        <div class="profile-book-copy"><div class="profile-book-meta" id="profileBookMeta1">第 2 卷 · 2016 · 扶桑社</div><h4 id="profileBookTitle1">《苍炎Ⅱ：飞翔篇》</h4><p id="profileBookDesc1">记录2012年至2016年的竞技历程，包括赴多伦多训练、索契冬奥夺冠、伤病与疾病，以及不断刷新世界纪录的过程。</p></div>
      </article>
      <article class="glass profile-book-card" data-book-index="2">
        <div class="profile-book-cover"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="./aoi-hono-cover-03.jpg?v=20260717b" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='./assets/book-aoi-hono-3.jpg?v=20260717b';" alt="《苍炎Ⅲ：究竟篇》封面"></div>
        <div class="profile-book-copy"><div class="profile-book-meta" id="profileBookMeta2">第 3 卷 · 2023 · 扶桑社</div><h4 id="profileBookTitle2">《苍炎Ⅲ：究竟篇》</h4><p id="profileBookDesc2">从2015—2016赛季休赛期写到2018年冬奥卫冕与2020年完成超级全满贯，呈现他对理想滑冰的持续追求。</p></div>
      </article>
      <article class="glass profile-book-card" data-book-index="3">
        <div class="profile-book-cover"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="./aoi-hono-cover-04.jpg?v=20260717b" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='./assets/book-aoi-hono-4.jpg?v=20260717b';" alt="《苍炎Ⅳ：无限篇》封面"></div>
        <div class="profile-book-copy"><div class="profile-book-meta" id="profileBookMeta3">第 4 卷 · 2023 · 扶桑社</div><h4 id="profileBookTitle3">《苍炎Ⅳ：无限篇》</h4><p id="profileBookDesc3">聚焦北京冬奥挑战四周半跳与竞技生涯的终章，并延伸至职业转向后的 PROLOGUE、GIFT 等全新创作。</p></div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="competitions" class="section"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head"><div><div class="section-label">Complete competition archive</div><h2>全部比赛档案</h2></div><p class="section-intro">完整收录已整理的比赛档案，可按阶段、年份、赛事类型、地点与奖牌检索。</p></div>
