      <div class="section-label">Japan vector boundary atlas</div>
      <h3>职业冰演宇宙 · 日本地图</h3>
      <p>这里换成完整日本矢量边界图，并标出 PROLOGUE、GIFT、RE_PRAY、notte stellata、Echoes of Life 等职业冰演抵达过的城市。筛选冰演系列后，对应城市与都道府县会点亮。</p>
      <div id="showMapEvents" class="show-map-events"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div><div class="filters" id="showFilters"><button class="filter active" data-show-filter="all">全部 36 场</button><button class="filter" data-show-filter="solo">个人叙事</button><button class="filter" data-show-filter="commemoration">纪念／慈善</button><button class="filter" data-show-filter="2026">2026 最新</button></div><div id="posterGrid" class="poster-grid" style="margin-top:22px"></div></div></section>




<section id="costumes" class="section wrap costume-museum-v2">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label" data-i18n="costumeLabel">Costume archive</div>
      <h2 data-i18n="costumeTitle">冰上服装与节目世界</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-intro" data-i18n="costumeIntro">从 2004–2022 的竞技节目考斯滕开始整理：按幼年／青年／成年阶段筛选，也可以直接选择曲目，看同一节目在不同赛季出现过的服装与关联比赛。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="costume-controls glass">
    <select id="costumePhase" aria-label="Costume phase">
      <option value="all" data-i18n="phaseAll">全部阶段</option>
      <option value="child" data-i18n="phaseChild">幼年组</option>
      <option value="junior" data-i18n="phaseJunior">青年组</option>
      <option value="senior" data-i18n="phaseSenior">成年组</option>
    </select>
    <select id="costumeProgram" aria-label="Program">
      <option value="all" data-i18n="programAll">全部曲目</option>
    </select>
    <button id="costumeToggle" class="btn" type="button" data-i18n="expandCostumes">展开更多</button>
  </div>
  <div class="glass costume-atlas">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label" data-i18n="programAtlasLabel">Program constellation</div>
      <h3 data-i18n="programAtlasTitle">曲目星图</h3>
      <p data-i18n="programAtlasIntro">点选曲目后，下方会集中显示该曲目的多套服装；右侧时间线会按节目使用赛季关联比赛档案。</p>
    </div>
    <div id="programStars" class="program-stars"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="costume-layout">
    <div>
      <div id="costumeCount" class="archive-count"></div>
      <div id="costumeGrid" class="costume-grid costume-grid-v2"></div>
    </div>
    <aside class="glass costume-timeline-panel">
      <div class="section-label" data-i18n="programTimelineLabel">Program timeline</div>
      <h3 id="costumeTimelineTitle" data-i18n="programTimelineTitle">选择曲目查看关联比赛</h3>
      <div id="costumeTimeline" class="costume-timeline"></div>
      <p class="costume-source-note"><span data-i18n="costumeSourceNote">图片目录来源：</span><a href="https://planethanyu.com/wiki/yuzuru-hanyu/yuzuru-hanyu-costumes/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Planet Hanyu Costume Archive ↗</a></p>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="sources" class="section wrap" data-stable-source-lang="zh"><div class="section-head"><div><h2>官方网站</h2></div><p class="section-intro">这里只放 ICE STORY 项目、成绩档案和服装资料入口。</p></div><div class="official-grid source-list"><article class="source-card glass"><h3>ICE STORY 与职业项目</h3><div class="source-list"><a href="https://prologue-official.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>PROLOGUE 官方网站<small>职业转向后的首个个人冰演</small></span><span>↗</span></a><a href="https://gift-official.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>GIFT 官方网站<small>Tokyo Dome 单人冰演</small></span><span>↗</span></a><a href="https://repray-icestory.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>RE_PRAY 官方网站<small>ICE STORY 第二章</small></span><span>↗</span></a><a href="https://echoesoflife.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>Echoes of Life 官方网站<small>ICE STORY 2024–2025</small></span><span>↗</span></a><a href="https://realive-icestory.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>REALIVE 官方网站<small>ICE STORY 项目入口</small></span><span>↗</span></a><a href="https://nottestellata.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>notte stellata 官方网站<small>纪念 / 慈善演出系列</small></span><span>↗</span></a></div></article><article class="source-card glass"><h3>成绩档案与资料</h3><div class="source-list"><a href="https://www.olympics.com/en/athletes/yuzuru-hanyu" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>Olympics 官方运动员档案<small>冬奥资料入口</small></span><span>↗</span></a><a href="https://www.isu.org/figure-skating/entries-results/fsk-results" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>ISU 官方成绩档案<small>国际滑联赛事结果入口</small></span><span>↗</span></a><a href="https://www.jsfresults.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>日本滑冰联盟成绩页<small>日本国内赛结果入口</small></span><span>↗</span></a><a href="https://planethanyu.com/wiki/yuzuru-hanyu/yuzuru-hanyu-costumes/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>Planet Hanyu 服装图鉴<small>考斯滕参考入口</small></span><span>↗</span></a></div></article></div></section>
  </main>

  <footer><div class="footer-contact"><strong>管理员联系方式</strong><span>X：@Momoka_941207</span><span>小红书：HY941207_66</span></div><div class="footer-meta">羽生结弦 · ICE LEGACY 数字展览 · 数据范围 1994—2026</div></footer>
  <div id="tooltip" class="tooltip"></div>
  <div id="modal" class="modal" aria-hidden="true"><div class="modal-card"><div id="modalHero" class="modal-hero"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" id="modalImage" alt="官方主视觉"><button id="modalClose" class="close" aria-label="关闭">×</button><div class="modal-title"><div id="modalOverline" class="overline"></div><h2 id="modalTitle"></h2></div></div><div id="modalBody" class="modal-body"></div></div></div>

  <script>
    const annual=[[2004,3,0],[2005,3,0],[2006,3,0],[2007,9,0],[2008,8,0],[2009,11,0],[2010,6,0],[2011,7,0],[2012,6,0],[2013,7,0],[2014,7,0],[2015,7,0],[2016,5,0],[2017,5,0],[2018,4,0],[2019,6,0],[2020,2,0],[2021,3,0],[2022,1,5],[2023,0,6],[2024,0,13],[2025,0,7],[2026,0,5]];
    const shows=[
      {id:'prologue',title:'PROLOGUE',year:'2022',category:'solo',count:5,image:'assets/inline-00-964c04ae5f.png',url:'https://prologue-official.jp/',intro:'职业转向后的首个自我制作单人冰演，以“序章”为名回望滑冰生涯，也为之后的故事打开入口。',role:'出演／制作',performances:[['2022-11-04','ぴあアリーナMM','横滨'],['2022-11-05','ぴあアリーナMM','横滨'],['2022-12-02','FLAT HACHINOHE','八户'],['2022-12-03','FLAT HACHINOHE','八户'],['2022-12-05','FLAT HACHINOHE','八户']]},
      {id:'gift',title:'GIFT at Tokyo Dome',year:'2023',category:'solo',count:1,image:'assets/inline-00-f613b469f5.jpg',url:'https://gift-official.jp/',intro:'首个在东京巨蛋举行的单人冰演。羽生结弦担任制作总指挥，以冰上故事表达自己的过去与未来。',role:'制作总指挥／出演',performances:[['2023-02-26','Tokyo Dome','东京']]},
      {id:'notte',title:'notte stellata',year:'2023—2026',category:'commemoration',count:12,image:'assets/inline-00-45302c6fe6.jpg',url:'https://nottestellata.com/',intro:'从东日本大震灾的记忆出发，以“星月夜”象征黑暗中的希望；由羽生结弦与多位滑冰者共同传递来自灾区的光。',role:'座长／领衔滑冰者',performances:[['2023-03-10','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2023-03-11','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2023-03-12','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2024-03-08','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2024-03-09','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2024-03-10','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2025-03-07','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2025-03-08','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2025-03-09','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2026-03-07','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2026-03-08','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2026-03-09','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府']]},
      {id:'repray',title:'RE_PRAY TOUR',year:'2023—2024',category:'solo',count:8,image:'assets/inline-00-aac0a6c0d6.png',url:'https://repray-icestory.jp/',intro:'首个个人巡演。作品把游戏世界中的伦理与价值观带入 ICE STORY，围绕生命、选择、孤独与祈愿展开。',role:'出演／制作总指挥',performances:[['2023-11-04','Saitama Super Arena','埼玉'],['2023-11-05','Saitama Super Arena','埼玉'],['2024-01-12','SAGA Arena','佐贺'],['2024-01-14','SAGA Arena','佐贺'],['2024-02-17','ぴあアリーナMM','横滨'],['2024-02-19','ぴあアリーナMM','横滨'],['2024-04-07','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2024-04-09','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府']]},
      {id:'charity',title:'Noto Charity Performance',year:'2024',category:'commemoration',count:1,image:'assets/inline-00-4f4d4394ab.jpg',url:'https://www.olympics.com/en/news/hanyu-yuzuru-back-kanazawa-figure-skating-earthquake',intro:'为能登半岛地震灾区举办的复兴支援慈善演出。相关信息由 Olympics 官方报道核对。',role:'主持／出演',performances:[['2024-09-15','石川／金泽地区','金泽']]},
      {id:'echoes',title:'Echoes of Life TOUR',year:'2024—2025',category:'solo',count:7,image:'assets/inline-00-0eb65c133c.png',url:'https://echoesoflife.jp/',intro:'ICE STORY 第三部，以“生命与人生之问”为核心，把二十五年滑冰生涯累积的身体表达与情感经验写入大型巡演。',role:'出演／制作总指挥',performances:[['2024-12-07','Saitama Super Arena','埼玉'],['2024-12-09','Saitama Super Arena','埼玉'],['2024-12-11','Saitama Super Arena','埼玉'],['2025-01-03','Hiroshima Green Arena','广岛'],['2025-01-05','Hiroshima Green Arena','广岛'],['2025-02-07','LaLa arena TOKYO-BAY','船桥'],['2025-02-09','LaLa arena TOKYO-BAY','船桥']]},
      {id:'realive',title:'REALIVE',year:'2026',category:'solo',count:2,image:'assets/inline-00-ff07f3ee65.png',url:'https://realive-icestory.jp/',intro:'把过去创作的节目重新作为“活着的存在”带回此刻；强调现场不可重复的时间、身体与观众共同生成的新记忆。',role:'艺术家／制作总指挥',performances:[['2026-04-11','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府'],['2026-04-12','Sekisui Heim Super Arena','利府']]}
    ];
    const milestones=[
      {year:'1994-12-07',category:'人生',title:'出生于仙台',text:'羽生结弦出生于日本宫城县仙台市。',image:'assets/inline-00-60a51d862a.jpg',url:'https://isu-skating.com/figure-skating/skaters/yuzuru-hanyu/',credit:'羽生结弦官方 Instagram 公开的幼年滑冰照 · ITmedia ねとらぼ转载',imageUrl:'https://nlab.itmedia.co.jp/cont/articles/3344311/'},
      {year:'1999',category:'人生',title:'开始滑冰',text:'ISU 官方档案记录其于 1999 年开始学习花样滑冰。',image:'assets/inline-00-b19bb86ed7.jpg',url:'https://isu-skating.com/figure-skating/skaters/yuzuru-hanyu/',credit:'中村康一 / Image Works · 2004 全日本 Novice · Walker Plus',imageUrl:'https://www.walkerplus.com/trend/matome/article/194208/'},
      {year:'2014',category:'竞技',title:'索契冬奥会冠军',text:'获得男子单人滑金牌，成为首位夺得冬奥男单冠军的日本选手。',image:'assets/inline-00-6c6e8fbf50.jpg',url:'https://www.olympics.com/en/athletes/yuzuru-hanyu',credit:'David W. Carmichael · 2014 Sochi Winter Olympics · CC BY-SA 3.0 / Wikimedia Commons',imageUrl:'https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:2014_Winter_Olympics_-_Yuzuru_Hanyu_SP.jpg'},
      {year:'2015',category:'纪录',title:'总分首次突破 300',text:'NHK Trophy 总分 322.40；ISU 档案记载其成为首位总分超过 300 分的选手。',image:'assets/inline-00-e6b0e5f297.jpg',url:'https://isu-skating.com/figure-skating/skaters/yuzuru-hanyu/',credit:'Phantom Kabocha · 2015–16 Grand Prix Final · CC BY 4.0 / Wikimedia Commons',imageUrl:'https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:2015_Grand_Prix_Final_-_Yuzuru_Hanyu_SP_(2).jpg'},
      {year:'2016',category:'纪录',title:'干净完成后外结环四周跳',text:'ISU 档案记载其成为首位在比赛中完成干净四周 Loop 的选手。',image:'assets/inline-00-7460ff6eac.jpg',url:'https://isu-skating.com/figure-skating/skaters/yuzuru-hanyu/',credit:'Phantom Kabocha · 2016–17 Grand Prix Final · Wikimedia Commons',imageUrl:'https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:2016_Grand_Prix_Final_-_Yuzuru_Hanyu_SP_(1).jpg'},
      {year:'2018',category:'竞技',title:'平昌冬奥会卫冕',text:'连续两届获得男子单人滑金牌，完成半个多世纪未见的冬奥男单卫冕。',image:'assets/inline-00-1ecc67ed1e.jpg',url:'https://www.olympics.com/en/athletes/yuzuru-hanyu',credit:'Getty Images · 2018 PyeongChang · published by ISU',imageUrl:'https://isu-skating.com/figure-skating/news/figure-skatings-most-iconic-olympic-moments/'},
      {year:'2022',category:'竞技',title:'北京冬奥会',text:'第三次参加冬奥会，男子单人滑排名第四。',image:'assets/inline-00-3ce9357065.jpg',url:'https://www.olympics.com/en/athletes/yuzuru-hanyu',credit:'Getty Images · Beijing 2022 Men Single Skating · Beijing official portal',imageUrl:'https://english.beijing.gov.cn/beijing2022/photos/202202/t20220209_2606862.html'},
      {year:'2022-11',category:'职业',title:'PROLOGUE',text:'职业阶段首个单人冰演系列开启。',image:'assets/inline-00-964c04ae5f.png',url:'https://prologue-official.jp/'},
      {year:'2023-02-26',category:'职业',title:'GIFT at Tokyo Dome',text:'史上首次在东京巨蛋举行的单人冰演。',image:'assets/inline-00-f613b469f5.jpg',url:'https://gift-official.jp/'},
      {year:'2023—2024',category:'职业',title:'RE_PRAY TOUR',text:'首个个人巡演，四站共八场。',image:'assets/inline-00-aac0a6c0d6.png',url:'https://repray-icestory.jp/'},
      {year:'2024—2025',category:'职业',title:'Echoes of Life TOUR',text:'ICE STORY 第三部，工作簿收录七场。',image:'assets/inline-00-0eb65c133c.png',url:'https://echoesoflife.jp/'},
      {year:'2026',category:'职业',title:'REALIVE 与 notte stellata',text:'职业表达继续延伸至新的 ICE STORY project 与纪念冰演。',image:'assets/inline-00-ff07f3ee65.png',url:'https://realive-icestory.jp/'}
    ];
    const $=s=>document.querySelector(s),NS='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg',tip=$('#tooltip');
    const svgEl=(n,a={})=>{const x=document.createElementNS(NS,n);Object.entries(a).forEach(([k,v])=>x.setAttribute(k,v));return x};
    function hover(node,html){node.addEventListener('mousemove',e=>{tip.innerHTML=html;tip.style.left=(e.clientX+12)+'px';tip.style.top=(e.clientY-18)+'px';tip.style.opacity=1});node.addEventListener('mouseleave',()=>tip.style.opacity=0)}
    function drawTrend(){const chartLang=document.documentElement.dataset.lang||'zh',chartText={zh:{aria:'年度活动轨迹',competition:'比赛记录',shows:'职业冰演'},en:{aria:'Annual activity trajectory',competition:'Competition records',shows:'Professional ice shows'},ja:{aria:'年間活動の軌跡',competition:'競技記録',shows:'プロアイスショー'}}[chartLang]||{aria:'年度活动轨迹',competition:'比赛记录',shows:'职业冰演'},box=$('#trend'),W=920,H=350,p={l:42,r:18,t:26,b:42},max=14,svg=svgEl('svg',{viewBox:`0 0 ${W} ${H}`,role:'img','aria-label':chartText.aria});for(let v=0;v<=max;v+=2){const py=p.t+(H-p.t-p.b)*(1-v/max);svg.append(svgEl('line',{x1:p.l,y1:py,x2:W-p.r,y2:py,class:'gridline'}));const t=svgEl('text',{x:p.l-8,y:py+3,'text-anchor':'end',class:'axis-text'});t.textContent=v;svg.append(t)}const x=i=>p.l+i*(W-p.l-p.r)/(annual.length-1),y=v=>p.t+(H-p.t-p.b)*(1-v/max);[[1,'#55c7f2',chartText.competition],[2,'#f1874b',chartText.shows]].forEach(([idx,c,name])=>{svg.append(svgEl('path',{d:annual.map((d,i)=>(i?'L':'M')+x(i)+' '+y(d[idx])).join(' '),class:'line',stroke:c,style:`color:${c}`}));annual.forEach((d,i)=>{const q=svgEl('circle',{cx:x(i),cy:y(d[idx]),r:4.5,fill:c,class:'dot'});hover(q,`<b>${d[0]}</b><br>${name}：${d[idx]}`);svg.append(q)})});annual.forEach((d,i)=>{if(i%2===0){const t=svgEl('text',{x:x(i),y:H-12,'text-anchor':'middle',class:'axis-text'});t.textContent=d[0];svg.append(t)}});box.replaceChildren(svg)}
    function renderPosters(filter='all'){const list=shows.filter(s=>filter==='all'||filter==='2026'&&s.year.includes('2026')||s.category===filter);$('#posterGrid').innerHTML=list.map(s=>`<article class="poster" data-show-id="${s.id}" tabindex="0"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="${s.image}" alt="${s.title} 官方主视觉"><div class="arrow">↗</div><div class="poster-content"><div class="poster-meta"><span>${s.year}</span><span>${s.count} 场</span></div><h3>${s.title}</h3><p>${s.intro}</p></div></article>`).join('');document.querySelectorAll('[data-show-id]').forEach(card=>{const open=()=>openShow(card.dataset.showId);card.addEventListener('click',open);card.addEventListener('keydown',e=>{if(e.key==='Enter')open()})})}
    function renderMilestones(filter='all'){const list=milestones.filter(m=>filter==='all'||m.category===filter);$('#milestoneCount').textContent=`显示 ${list.length} / ${milestones.length} 个节点`;$('#milestoneGrid').innerHTML=list.length?list.map((m,i)=>`<article class="milestone-card" data-mile-index="${milestones.indexOf(m)}" tabindex="0"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="${m.image}" alt="${m.title} 官方图片"><div class="milestone-body"><div class="milestone-year">${m.year} · ${m.category}</div><h3>${m.title}</h3><p>${m.text}</p></div></article>`).join(''):'<div class="empty">此分类暂无记录</div>';document.querySelectorAll('[data-mile-index]').forEach(card=>{const open=()=>openMilestone(+card.dataset.mileIndex);card.addEventListener('click',open);card.addEventListener('keydown',e=>{if(e.key==='Enter')open()})})}
    function openShow(id){const s=shows.find(x=>x.id===id);$('#modalImage').src=s.image;$('#modalImage').alt=s.title+' 官方主视觉';$('#modalOverline').textContent=`PROFESSIONAL ICE SHOW · ${s.year} · ${s.count} 场`;$('#modalTitle').textContent=s.title;$('#modalBody').innerHTML=`<div class="modal-copy"><div><p>${s.intro}</p><a class="official-link" href="${s.url}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">访问官方页面 ↗</a></div><div class="facts"><div class="fact"><span>Role</span><b>${s.role}</b></div><div class="fact"><span>Performances</span><b>${s.count} 场</b></div><div class="fact"><span>Image source</span><b>系列官网公开主视觉</b></div></div></div><div class="schedule"><h3>演出档案 · 当前收录 ${s.performances.length} 场</h3><div class="performance-list">${s.performances.map(p=>`<div class="performance"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="${s.image}" alt="${s.title} 官方主视觉"><div><b>${p[0]} · ${p[2]}</b><span>${p[1]}</span></div></div>`).join('')}</div></div>`;openModal()}
    function openMilestone(index){const m=milestones[index];$('#modalImage').src=m.image;$('#modalImage').alt=m.title+' 官方图片';$('#modalOverline').textContent=`MILESTONE · ${m.category} · ${m.year}`;$('#modalTitle').textContent=m.title;$('#modalBody').innerHTML=`<div class="modal-copy"><div><p>${m.text}</p><p></p>${m.credit?`<p class="image-credit">图片：${m.credit}</p><a class="official-link" href="${m.imageUrl}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">查看图片来源与授权 ↗</a>`:''}<a class="official-link" href="${m.url}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">查看事件来源 ↗</a></div><div class="facts"><div class="fact"><span>Year / Date</span><b>${m.year}</b></div><div class="fact"><span>Category</span><b>${m.category}</b></div><div class="fact"><span>Verification</span><b></b></div></div></div>`;openModal()}
    function openModal(){$('#modal').classList.add('open');$('#modal').setAttribute('aria-hidden','false');document.body.style.overflow='hidden'}function closeModal(){$('#modal').classList.remove('open');$('#modal').setAttribute('aria-hidden','true');document.body.style.overflow=''}
    $('#modalClose').addEventListener('click',closeModal);$('#modal').addEventListener('click',e=>{if(e.target===$('#modal'))closeModal()});document.addEventListener('keydown',e=>{if(e.key==='Escape')closeModal()});
