      ["1994-12-07 · Life", "Born in Sendai", "Yuzuru Hanyu was born in Sendai, Miyagi, Japan."],
      ["1999 · Life", "Started skating", "He began learning figure skating at around age four."],
      ["2014 · Competition", "Sochi Olympic champion", "He won the men's singles gold medal and became Japan's first Olympic men's singles champion."],
